    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell. I\u2019ve totally babied this ride, but I\u2019m ready to pass it on to someone who will love it just as much as I have. If you're looking for a dream car that looks and drives perfectly, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
