      "description": "Offering an impeccable E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits zero subframe cracking and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing and rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical reliability. The naturally aspirated induction through individual throttle bodies provides instantaneous throttle response, paired with a crisp six-speed longitudinal manual transmission. The exterior retains its factory-original finish with no evidence of panel misalignment or oxidation, while the chassis remains compliant yet surgically precise. Complete with a documented service history and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
